[recto] Death of Virgin. [Arthur E.] Popham, Etchings of Margaret of Austria by Hogenberg and Van Orley, The Print Collector's Quarterly, XVI, 1929, pp. 279-284, Pl.I, p. 278, Pl.II, p.281, citaten pp. 280, 282; [verso] [vervolg]; [toegevoegde vermelding]: Parallel Lugt in [Paul Bergmans et al., ed.], Mélanges Hulin de Loo, Italië en het Noorden, [Bruxelles: Librairie nationale d'art et d'histoire], 1931, 245-248 has shown that a drawing in the Louvre attributed to N. Hogenberg is based on Marcantonio's Plague.
